Notes for folder structure.

--> layout
Nav, Footer, Side menu etc get all defined in layout folder

--> pages, component
Use the folder page for creating pages of app.
Create the page name folder in Components folder and define all components in that folder.

--> utils
everything that help with the web app is included in this folder like, constants, helper function, static data, etc.

--> store images that are being used by react components in /src/assets

--> store images that are being not used by react components ie favicons.

--> Libraries
-> Tailwind for styling
-> React-query for state management and fetching with axios.
-> React-icons if same icon is available in react icons library.
-> Yup for form validation
-> React router dom for routing.
